	<p>To perform validation on a SurrealQL local file, in a terminal run the <Ascua::Prism::Inline @language="shell" @code="surreal validate" /> command with the required argument.</p>
	<codes vertical>
		<Code @name="docs-cli-validate-main.shell" text="Command line">
			user@localhost % surreal validate [PATTERN]
		</Code>
	</codes>
